OL,7,FA woman says she's devastated after
OL,8,Fher grandmother's gravestone was taken
OL,9,Ffrom her resting place.
OL,11,FCherie Pontin said they've searched
OL,12,FGravesend Cemetery but it's nowhere to
OL,13,Fbe found.
OL,15,FGravesham Borough Council is
OL,16,Fsupporting the family and said a theft
OL,17,Fof this kind is extremely rare.
