OL,7,FAll the family are absolutely
OL,8,Fdevastated."
OL,10,FThe family first noticed that the
OL,11,Fgravestone was missing during a visit
OL,12,Fin the middle of November.
OL,14,FThey are now looking at replacing the
OL,15,Fstone, but say it could take months to
OL,16,Fbe put in place.
OL,18,F"It is something that we're looking
OL,19,Finto with regards to the cost and
OL,20,Fwhether it's affordable for us to do
OL,21,Fthat," Cherie added.
