OL,7,F"But the issue that we have right now,
OL,8,Fwhich is very difficult, it's
OL,9,FChristmas time, and the people that
OL,10,Fmake the stones have advised us it
OL,11,Fwould be at least 12 weeks, if not
OL,12,Fmore, to be able to replace it."
OL,14,FThe cemetery has offered to put a
OL,15,Fcross and some flowers down but Cherie
OL,16,Fsays the family are worried it could
OL,17,Fhappen again.
