OL,7,F"We really need to have awareness, and
OL,8,Fpeople need to be vigilant when
OL,9,Fthey're coming to the grave site and
OL,10,Fto have a look around, and if they see
OL,11,Fanything strange, to let the cemetery
OL,12,Fknow."
OL,14,FGravesham Borough council's grounds
OL,15,Fstaff have searched the area and the
OL,16,Ffamily has been offeed a temporary
OL,17,Fcross to mark the resting place.
OL,19,FMary Bobby from Gravesham Borough
OL,20,FCouncil said: "It's extremely rare.
