OL,7,F"Occasionally a little trinket might
OL,8,Fget moved around, but in the 10 years,
OL,9,Fi've worked for GBC i've never seen
OL,10,Fsomething that has come up before so
OL,11,Fit's very very rare.
OL,13,F"They have very little value - once
OL,14,Fthey are inscribed. and they cant be
OL,15,Fused for other people's graves so
OL,16,Fthere's no rhyme or reason for doing
OL,17,Fit."
